cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper proposes a method for building efficient compact CNN-based networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the performance of the proposed method, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper presents experimental results on image datasets, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM).
